Version 1.7.1 - 2011-05-05 (stable)
----------------------------------------
Notes:
  * Fixed a bug when the status component of the HTTP response is missing
  (fixes Bug #19390) (Ilia) * Fixed double-free when auto-decompressing pages
  (Ilia) * Fixed non-funtional HttpMessage::setResponseStatus() * Fixed Bug
  #22177 (http_redirect breaks output with zlib.output_compression=on) *
  Fixed Bug #17806 (Segmentation fault when passing invalid url to
  http_get()) * Fixed logic error and possible hang in sapi_deactivate when
  using http_get_request_body() with a request body longer than 4096 bytes
  (Rob) * Fixed Bug #17896 (Make failed)

